nodes.bodyText: We should add some log to the validation process

Since the validationResultBuilder is passed in as a parameter, we cannot be sure that there is no validation result in it. Currently it would be ok to use as you suggest, but later on if a validation is added before the invocation of the method I think a developer can easily forget about downstream used ValidationResult.empty usages.
What do you think?
